{"tid":2477735,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"[樂理]《2020年代香港流行曲和弦編曲賞析》","createTime":"2021-04-06T13:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T19:24:59.000Z","uid":56674,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1802247bb7f402e48226c9e6508c9e152eb618","tid":2477735,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係蘭調人，我係一個全職既結他老師，有任何野想問我可以透過telegram搵到我： <a href=\"https://t.me/Guitar_ABC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGuitar_ABC&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXta7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=516cb6f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Guitar_ABC</a> <br />\n<br />\n繼上幾次只係寫關於結他既內容，今次出文係想分享我對最新本地流行曲既chord progression同編曲既分析同睇法。為左可以跟得上時代，細佬我主要會響呢度寫最新出既廣東歌。是次帖文重點： <br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 將最新出既流行曲，最hit既派台歌，既chord精準地執一次出黎。 <br />\n2. 除左係有chord名之外，我會寫埋禁法最好既位置，同埋相對無咁似但會比較容易禁既形狀。 <br />\n3. 某d重要，常見於廣東歌既chord progression如果有出現的話（8成有），會大概解析比大家聽。大家總會試過聽一首歌時，硬係覺得好似以前響唔知邊度聽過，背後原因就係呢度：某兩三套chord係咁出現 <br />\n4. 點樣可以識得分你睇緊果份譜d chord岩唔岩 <br />\n5. 點樣聽chord，執歌，learn any songs by ear，就算你無perfect pitch <br />\n6. 好聽既旋律係點運作？有chord先定有旋律先？ </strong> <br />\n<br />\n而我同大家一樣，以前岩岩開始學樂器既時候聽到一首歌好聽，想彈，網上搵譜，好多譜彈落去都唔係太似原本首歌，甚至直頭有d chord聽落去係執錯左（當然有時係要轉個禁法就會岩番，未必每次都係譜上面寫果個chord唔岩）。就算係一d本身有考過級既人黎講，跟住譜彈就得，但如果要好有脈絡執番哂成首（你鐘意聽既）歌既chord出黎，然後彈出黎順，都好似唔太容易。而大前提係要有最基本既樂理知識先，所以黎緊出既文，頭幾段會先寫：  <br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. Chord 基本組成規則，Chord groups <br />\n2. Chord既先後次序應該係點樣決定：Cadence <br />\n3. 邊啲chord係會比較經常放埋一齊：Diatonic Harmony <br />\n4. 同一組既chord點排列先至會產生最順耳既感覺：Circle of 5th <br />\n5. 將同一個chord彈得最好／最接近原著既禁法：CAGED system</strong>  <br />\n<br />\n礙於帖文長度設計，太基本既樂理知識就唔會響度詳細寫（eg. 音樂系統12個音係點分法，major scale點組成）。而基於我係一個結他人，所以主要會響度give out既內容都係用guitar fretboard 6條線咁既格式去表達。最基本既open chord禁法之類都不會在此詳述，詳情可以自己google。如果去到中途有d比較高階既樂理要解釋，就會響果首歌既分析中途插入。所以今次寫既野係適合初階，有基本結他概念／已經可以簡單自彈自唱的人仕。 <br />\n<br />\n之後盡可能做到課餘時間每日一連載，每日一update，多謝大家收睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf2888253ccdf7d4c5895b4e5d59b002dd7ad52","tid":2477735,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9aa8c524bcff6cb80e86e9190c457737caa64b1","tid":2477735,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"分析邊首先"},{"pid":"fcbf0d3f8cfe634f296db00c5278a778556351c9","tid":2477735,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9aa8c524bcff6cb80e86e9190c457737caa64b1","tid":2477735,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"分析邊首先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"寫哂前面就出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bc95360fe8f24e374d578bd69502825d679ee2","tid":2477735,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcbf0d3f8cfe634f296db00c5278a778556351c9","tid":2477735,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9aa8c524bcff6cb80e86e9190c457737caa64b1","tid":2477735,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"分析邊首先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"寫哂前面就出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T15:13:35.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829dae0647542070b6d391806fd0a23a37e7649c","tid":2477735,"uid":129770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"lm先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fec1dd24a8e5cfbdfde2937dccf6731ca1302c","tid":2477735,"uid":71194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b20f08f8215fffeefacfe5305ebdd0dda3d10b5c","tid":2477735,"uid":56674,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:28:20.000Z","msg":"<ins>1. Chord groups - 和弦分類</ins><br />\n 先在此簡介，以下落黎會講既呢套方法係可以唔需要識得數一個音階入面既音名，只需要識數度數就可以，同classical要記得scale 音名彈得番出黎係兩回事。原因係結他指板係2D平面，鋼琴琴鍵係1D，一條線用黑白鍵左右延伸。結他可以透過記形狀就可以達到同其他樂器同一樣既工作目的，比較容易上手（如果你對數字比較敏感，數得快）。<br />\n<br />\n正式開始，先將以下落黎會用既數字解釋一下： <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/07/oFbLHJ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F07%2FoFbLHJ.jpeg&h=26225332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大調音階中會有既7個音（大家最常既叫法：Do Re Mi Fa Sol La Ti）將會以1234567表示。當然，大家需要具備基本數音階既能力。C大調就係C-D-E-F-G-A-B，Ab大調就係Ab-Bb-C-Db-Eb-F-G，如此類推。但以下落黎，為左可以只用一套方法而可以通行於每一隻歌之上，用數字就係最有效，最精簡既方法去理解同組織不同既砌圖。  <br />\n<br />\n換而言之，所有響現代音樂系統入面，會用到既數字，都係建基於major scale全全半全全全半既特性上。  <br />\n<br />\n其他既度數又如何呢？佢地都係游走響以上既1234567之間而存在，除左Mi-Fa（3-4)同Ti-Do（7-1)之外，其他既度數之間都存在一個音，將各自既全度分開一半。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/07/Q8XsRP.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F07%2FQ8XsRP.jpeg&h=4a938a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢5個音 (b2, b3, b5, b6, b7)就會將音樂系統，由只係得開心既major，延伸到有其他既組別：<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/07/RJ0ebP.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F07%2FRJ0ebP.jpeg&h=ecb4f011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上就係音樂系統之中最基本既3組chord group：Major， Minor同Dominant。  <br />\n<br />\n但咁樣都未係之後講流行曲寫法最重要，最實用既分組。實用上要睇得明廣東歌既寫法，要再將以上3組分成：Consonant同Dissonant<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">Consonant group：Major，Minor （聽上去比較順耳，祥和） <br />\nDissonant group：Dominant（聽上去有種恐怖感，outside sounding）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n定義既規則：果個triad或arpeggios是否擁有tri-tone（相差6個半度的音程，被認為係音樂系統上至陰至邪既音程）。而響Dominant 7th arpeggios之中，3-b7呢兩個音響半度圈上係相差6個半度，所以Dominant 7th係算係Dissonant。  <br />\n<br />\n最後，響最常見既triad當中，仲有最後兩個：  <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/07/zby4DR.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F07%2Fzby4DR.jpeg&h=83bbdaf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦都係最多人唔明有咩用／較少用／較難理解既triad，詳細解釋先唔寫住，但你見佢咁多flat咁多sharp，都應該係唔會聽落去太順耳，而順理成章地，佢地係屬於Dominant 7th果組，響香港流行曲佢地成日都會出現，不過就係會以某種dominant 7th出現（為免太驚嚇，仔細以咩形式會出現將會響後面講到果隻有先講）。  <br />\n<br />\n最後，簡約概括呢一組，響廣東歌編曲之中會用到既chord分類： <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/07/ElWCz1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F07%2FElWCz1.jpeg&h=b1d2667d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc499c8acf7811e59219db66738f412205558799","tid":2477735,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:41:49.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"ba9268024004d12aa746e97b44980ab95217daa4","tid":2477735,"uid":289186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"好實用！樓主加油！"},{"pid":"a89362c3b96988dd6538a8d5522405648322c298","tid":2477735,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"諗咗好耐蘭調喺邊度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1a9b19368922ca17e51ea93d3b6f743bc3ab10","tid":2477735,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm"},{"pid":"d73b4563390bf1587baa276fb08d7dcedad96d0a","tid":2477735,"uid":357250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:27:21.000Z","msg":"More<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b877a8044f505c5b411be777621e26679a89e661","tid":2477735,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e31357c89e1afbb6f7ece3bfbda8cbfd3da16c","tid":2477735,"uid":56674,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:22:32.000Z","msg":"<ins>2. Cadence － 和弦行走次序 </ins><br />\n理解完Chord有兩大組別後（Consonant, Dissonant），就需要知道呢兩組chord係應該點配對。廣東歌最重要既係歌詞，要膾炙人口，然後用旋律同和弦去配對，遷就出成首歌。而絕大部分流行曲要出到果套歌詞，和弦就必需要係以梅花間竹既方法將呢兩組chord配對：  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">Consonant -&gt; Dissonant -&gt; Consonant -&gt; Dissonant -&gt; .....  </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n例如《囍帖街》Chorus： <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/08/CV2UeD.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F08%2FCV2UeD.jpeg&h=60ff8897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第1, 3, 5, 7小節都係Major或minor，所以係屬於Consonant（都有部分major同minor係有少許dissonant，但主體係consonant），第2，4 ，6，8小節都係Dominant 7th（第2小節既G原本係G7，可以彈G7，但無G咁夾）。然後再循環一次。  <br />\n<br />\n填詞黎講，Consonant - Dissonant交換底下咁寫，係會順好多易寫好多。篇幅有限未能詳述"},{"pid":"b82d446ff3127aecc3053e54b85e3f58062631dc","tid":2477735,"uid":37347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T04:07:18.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d312259c70739bb3a4a6d231064d60882f82b45c","tid":2477735,"uid":59249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T06:51:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"88f525b885034b4f5190d54b77cb64f4e8444c6e","tid":2477735,"uid":43971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9264dea8d6953d510c0815c80ed5ea6c190ac080","tid":2477735,"uid":60441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T12:23:17.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"a2268a06b2d238e4e18e7f2ebcb81a85b376903a","tid":2477735,"uid":357250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T01:16:45.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"2940b780ac5af2e0bf3fd96c8883fea1e4e07e07","tid":2477735,"uid":286193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"有冇玩開fingerstyle 可唔可以露兩手<br />\n市面上太多太多沽名釣譽既結他佬呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba7cec6bd9e59a214d4dcd2c863eaad9363216f","tid":2477735,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2940b780ac5af2e0bf3fd96c8883fea1e4e07e07","tid":2477735,"uid":286193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"有冇玩開fingerstyle 可唔可以露兩手<br />\n市面上太多太多沽名釣譽既結他佬呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T02:45:46.000Z","msg":"樂理編曲, 最緊要講得明姐"},{"pid":"c1a5f7491c1fd28e1607d461ee3bdadbaa916988","tid":2477735,"uid":286193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dba7cec6bd9e59a214d4dcd2c863eaad9363216f","tid":2477735,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2940b780ac5af2e0bf3fd96c8883fea1e4e07e07","tid":2477735,"uid":286193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"有冇玩開fingerstyle 可唔可以露兩手<br />\n市面上太多太多沽名釣譽既結他佬呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T02:45:46.000Z","msg":"樂理編曲, 最緊要講得明姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T06:04:13.000Z","msg":"想學 樂理係要 <br />\n唔通你撚結他出去同人講樂理 但係自己彈到pet屎咁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ce6a2d86f3af951aebf9dfc4b010ea9cf4accb","tid":2477735,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"<ins>3. Diatonic Harmony 和弦的選擇</ins><br />\n水響0度結冰，100度變蒸氣，chord既行走方式一樣，響某個溫度同階段後一定要以某一個形態繼續行走，先至可以令到成個progression可以保持固定循環向前進。Diatonic Harmony即係將可以完成一個標準循環既chord匯集埋一齊。只係用呢個Harmony之中的成員去組成一個progression就可以產生最basic最順耳既感覺： <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/12/slNHSI.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F12%2FslNHSI.jpeg&h=559a66d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正因為為以上所有和弦既組成音都係來自於 I major scale，所以就稱之為Diatonic（同調性的）Harmony。Harmony動詞係Harmonize，即係將一堆單音以特定方式挑選，組合一齊表達，以產生和諧感。而揀既方式，必定以stacking 3rds既形式挑選。Stacking 3rds即係話將音將major scale之中以梅花間竹既方法挑選，再順序排列。響major scale梅花間竹咁揀音，最後所有出現既音同音之間都必然係相距3個或4個半度，我地稱之為major 3rd同minor 3rd。Major 同minor chord既分別大體上就係差第3度（3 or b3)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/12/p4ToYn.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F12%2Fp4ToYn.jpeg&h=c2484779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上一口氣寫埋如果係想將Diatonic Harmony除左係以Major/minor方式表達外，如果想以7th arpeggios方式（即係major 7th, minor 7th, dominany 7th, minor 7th flat 5th)，應該係點揀音，就係響stacking 3rds既原則下再去多一個音，括號裡面就寫左。數到最右如果到盡頭就會再番番轉頭開始再數過。所以iim7數出黎係2-4-6-8,，8號係7號既下一個，所以係1. 逢親係大過7既數字都減7就可以知道佢本身係咩度數。而最通用最好記必然係：  <br />\n<br />\n<strong>Major - minor - minor - Major - Major - minor - diminished </strong> <br />\n<br />\n香港流行曲由60年代到而家，最可以全盤理解睇哂都係用呢個口訣。7th arpeggios版本，只要理解做全部都係major變major 7 th，minor變minor 7th，係最後dim變成m7b5就可以。  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">Major 7th arpeggios: 1 3 5 7  <br />\n<br />\nminor 7th arpeggios: 1 b3 5 b7  <br />\n<br />\nDominant 7th arpeggios: 1 3 5 b7  <br />\n<br />\nminor 7th flat 5th arpeggios: 1 b3 b5 b7</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n點解普通maj-min-min-maj-maj-min-dim會變成maj7-m7-m7-maj7-7-m7-m7b5，特別係第5個chord要dominant，就必然要睇一路d音冧上去時，之間既距離變化：  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"green\">Major 7th arpeggios: 4H - 3H - 4H  <br />\n<br />\nminor 7th:arpeggios  3H - 4H - 3H  <br />\n<br />\nDominant 7th arpeggios: 4H - 3H - 3H  <br />\n<br />\nminor 7th flat 5th arpeggios: 3H - 3H - 4H  </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n只要細心核對番以上既1-3-5-7，2-4-6-8，之類既單音排列，數番佢地之間差幾多個半度，對應番個pattern同以上邊一組係吻合就可以  <br />\n<br />\n最後，以上你已經知道每一個diatonic member既組成音係咩（只用數字表達就可以，唔需要實音，因為要通用於所有key用數字就可以）。我地就會大致上以佢地既組成音相似性將七個不同既和弦組合成為3大組別： <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/12/elWrxY.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F12%2FelWrxY.jpeg&h=8be36fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCadence真正既格式就係：  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">Sub-dominant - Dominant - Tonic</span> </strong> <br />\n<br />\n所有香港流行曲和弦寫法全部都係跟住呢個規則。符合上一節所講的：Consonant - Dissonant - Consonant 原則。"},{"pid":"50a093d17bfff1140068cdd163dd32f1d0c7e480","tid":2477735,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T01:41:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bsOKs59nzXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbsOKs59nzXw&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXta7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=0cd09430\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bsOKs59nzXw</a><br />\n<br />\n睇開呢個 學到好多野<br />\n<br />\n樓主幾有心"},{"pid":"78ad990a1106724d16165fc6d8ebdf4ab3d04973","tid":2477735,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"2940b780ac5af2e0bf3fd96c8883fea1e4e07e07","tid":2477735,"uid":286193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"有冇玩開fingerstyle 可唔可以露兩手<br />\n市面上太多太多沽名釣譽既結他佬呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T01:42:55.000Z","msg":"睇李榮浩老師囉  <br />\n佢公認勁"},{"pid":"2df93acf43e32350fc3485f569407994de979133","tid":2477735,"uid":91933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T01:56:24.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9324ec84d55b5e22f8fb965988d6797a51cf083","tid":2477735,"uid":19986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s